frr_7bNBR5FBbe19qg">Tào Tháo</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Ph%E1%BA%A1t-%C4%91%C3%A0n-3/poem-W6iIbJRafGCVp8CSNb97ZA">Phạt đàn 3 - 伐檀 3</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thu-nh%E1%BA%ADt-Kinh-Nam-t%E1%BB%91ng-Th%E1%BA%A1ch-Th%E1%BB%A7-Ti%E1%BA%BFt-minh-ph%E1%BB%A7-t%E1%BB%AB-m%C3%A3n-c%C3%A1o-bi%E1%BB%87t-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-k%C3%BD-Ti%E1%BA%BFt-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-th%C6%B0-t%E1%BB%A5ng-%C4%91%E1%BB%A9c-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-Bfz7q1pPB52k-USL3w8zKg">Thu nhật Kinh Nam tống Thạch Thủ Tiết minh phủ từ mãn cáo biệt, phụng ký Tiết thượng thư tụng đức tự hoài phỉ nhiên chi tác, tam thập vận - 秋日荊南送石首薛明府辭滿告別奉寄薛尚書頌德敘懷斐然之作三十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/T%E1%BB%A9-thi%E1%BA%BFt-1/poem-1bzkHrZqz1OlRdsFmQZd5A">Tứ thiết 1 - 駟驖 1</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Xa-c%C3%B4ng-2/poem-r7NiuKKzKEYb6D7aQM9dYg">Xa công 2 - 車攻 2</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
